As someone specializing in finance, I'm highly interested in contributing to the growth and success of 1acre. I'd be grateful if you could share any information about potential opportunities at 1acre, especially those that might involve supporting expansion efforts or leveraging my finance background. Even if there aren't immediate openings in Bihar or Nagpur, I'd be interested in learning about opportunities at your headquarters in Telangana.
I've attached my phone number and email address .
9135509210
s2samarjeetkr@gmail.com

Amarjeet Kumar
